Compilation
-----------
$ mkdir build
$ cd build

$ cmake .. -DBOSP_PATH="/path/to/bbque" CMakeLists.txt
or 
$ cmake .. -DBOSP_PATH="/path/to/bbque" -DMANGO_ROOT="/path/to/mango/installation" CMakeLists
... if you want to specify an installation path different from "/"

$ make -jX	# Replace X with number of cores

Installation
-------------------
$ sudo make install
